单卡训练:
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=5 python -m torch.distributed.launch --nproc_per_node=1 --use_env train.py

多卡训练:
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=4,5 python -m torch.distributed.launch --nproc_per_node=2 --master_port=12345 train.py

保存checkpoint: --save

单卡测试:
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=5 python -m torch.distributed.launch --nproc_per_node=1 --use_env inference.py

多卡测试:
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=4,5 python -m torch.distributed.launch --nproc_per_node=2 --master_port=12345 inference.py